Business One is a clean, fully responsive theme, suitable for business sites, blogs, or portfolios. It is easily adaptable to your own ideas. 

This is my first commercial theme, so all comments are welcome. I will continue adding features and improving this theme, so if you have
any requests please get in touch.

Buy now for the introductory price of $10



jQuery 1.9.1 and Bootstrap 2.3.1


Page Templates
-----
* index page
* Single Blog Page
* Blog List
* Single Portfolio Page
* Portfolio Page using Isotope Masonry
* Contact Page

Main Features
-------------

* animated css for elegant animations
* pop up call back request form with form validation
* Font Awesome
* jquery isotope
* superfish menus
* sticky top menu
* A selection of Royalty free images
* Tested on IE9, IE10, Chrome, Firefox and Safari
* Sequence.js
* Easy to read js and css files, making customisation easier for you
* Dreamweaver Template file


